description: Returns an array of  RegexMatchSetSummary objects.

nested_items.name: NextMarker
nested_items.description: If you have more RegexMatchSet objects than the number that you specified for Limit in the request, the response includes a NextMarker value. To list more RegexMatchSet objects, submit another ListRegexMatchSets request, and specify the NextMarker value from the response in the NextMarker value in the next request.

nested_items.name: RegexMatchSetId
nested_items.description: The RegexMatchSetId for a RegexMatchSet. You use RegexMatchSetId to get information about a RegexMatchSet, update a RegexMatchSet, remove a RegexMatchSet from a Rule, and delete a RegexMatchSet from AWS WAF.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: A friendly name or description of the  RegexMatchSet. You can't change Name after you create a RegexMatchSet.
